original_title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Pest of the West
overview: Gather ‘round for a tale ‘bout SpongeBuck, a newbie who blew into Dead Eye Gulch fixin' to be the new fry cook only to find himself sheriff and goin' face-to-face, well, back-to-back since it was a duel, against the town's most dastardly denizen, Dead Eye Plankton. Can good triumph over evil in the Old West? Can a sponge make it in a town when he's outta food, water and lip balm?
title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Pest of the West
